No. 730,

Misc.

Trent v. United States. The Chief Justice, Mr. Justice Douglas and Mr. Justice Brennan are of the opinion that certiorari should be granted. Arthur J. Lambert and Richard A. Fitzgerald for petitioner. Solicitor General Cox, Acting Assistant Attorney General Foley, Beatrice Rosenberg and J. F. Bishop for the United States.

United States Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia Circuit. Certiorari denied.
